        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Tools to Educate All Children at Home Act or the TEACH Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises and temporarily increases the tax deduction for the expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers. Specifically, the deduction amount is increased from $250 to $1,000 in 2020 and 2021. </p>]]></text>
